Our Faculty & Program

Our Program

The Polymer Science and Technology Program at Mahidol University offers comprehensive graduate programs (Master's and Doctoral) designed to equip students with the knowledge and skills needed to excel in polymer science and related fields.

Our interdisciplinary approach combines theoretical foundations with practical applications, preparing our graduates for successful careers in academia, industry, and research.

Career Opportunities for Our Graduates

  • Senior Researchers and Developers in public and private sectors
  • University Professors and Academic Researchers
  • Principal Scientists, R&D Managers, and Directors in industry
  • Consultants and Advisors for various industries and governments
  • Innovators and Entrepreneurs in polymer technology
  • Policy Makers and Analysts shaping regulatory frameworks

Vision

To be a World-Class Faculty of Science with Social Impact

Mission

To be a leading Faculty of Science in education, research, and innovation of international quality, creating benefits for all humanity

Organizational Culture

Synergy for Success and Sustainability

Core Competencies

Potential in teaching and research in health sciences, fundamental sciences, and applied sciences
